ggxf utility plan


ggxf convert
ggxf import
ggxf metadata-template
ggxf describe
ggxf calculate
ggxf validate?
ggxf extract?

import uses 
import-formats.yaml, defining 
    * specific formats, ntv2, isg, ... with description, GDAL driver, parameters, metadata if possible, 
import-config.yaml 
    * default parameters for content types
    * parameters with default units
    * units with si conversion
    created from ggxf schema
metadata.yaml
  import uses metadata.yaml with template discovery metadata.  Can be exported for user to amend with metadata-template.  
  metadata content created from ggxf-schema (metadata field in GGXF entries).  Possibly generate some of import-config
 
Import can use --metadata user-file to set metadata.

implement import as another GGXF Reader module

describe includes option for --grid-extent-csv